snippet.title: [PS1] Planet Dob - psychedelic adventure from Hudson
snippet.description: A carefree space-traveling alien crash-lands on Earth where he is captured and forcibly taken to an Area 51-like facility to be experimented on. An Earthling test subject is selected for an incursion into the mind of the humanoid creature. And thus the adventure of a lifetime begins.
